-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/indian-oil-issues-second-tender-to-buy-crude-oil-for-september.html
Indian Oil Corp., the country’s
biggest refiner, issued its first tender for crude loading in
October, official documents obtained by Bloomberg News showed.  Last month, the company bought four cargoes totaling about
